title._content: Wereldreiziger vóór vertrek / Globe-trotter Willink with his overloaded moped

description._content: Nationaal Archief / Spaarnestad Photo, SFA002001986 Wereldreiziger Willink met zijn volgepakte bromfiets, vóór de Sint Bavo op de Grote Markt in Haarlem, 31 juli 1951. Hiker on moped, globe-trotter mr Willink with his overloaded moped in front of the St Bavo (church) on the Grote Markt - square in Haarlem. The Netherlands, 31 July 1951.
